📊 Data Catalog – Gold Layer
Overview

The Gold Layer represents the final, business-ready layer in the data warehouse. It is designed for analytics, reporting, and decision-making.

This layer contains dimension and fact views structured in a star schema, ensuring optimal performance and usability for BI tools and analysts.

Data State: Cleaned, transformed, and enriched
Data Model: Star Schema
Objects: Views (Dimensions & Facts)
Users: Analysts, BI Developers, Business Users
